Package model

Class Appointments

java.lang.Object
model.Appointments
Direct Known Subclasses:
ReportsDAO
public class Appointments extends Object
Appointments Model class that handles the logic and attributes of a given scheduled Appointment in the scheduler.

      public Appointments(int Appointment_ID, String Title, String Description, String Location, String Contact, String Type, LocalDateTime Start, LocalDateTime End, int Customer_ID, int User_ID, int Contact_ID)
      Constructor for the Appointments class.
      Parameters:
      Appointment_ID - = The ID of the given appointment.
      Title - = The name of the given appointment.
      Description - = The description of the given appointment.
      Location - = The location the appointment takes place.
      Contact - = The name of the given Contact at the appointment.
      Type - = The type of the given appointment.
      Start - = The starting time of the given appointment.
      End - = The ending time of the given appointment.
      Customer_ID - = The ID of the corresponding Customer.
      User_ID - = The ID of the corresponding User.
      Contact_ID - = The ID of the corresponding Contact.
